👑👵🔮🪞 "Mirror, mirror on the wall, who is the fairest of them all?" 🪞👑
🪞✨ "You, my Queen... but Snow White is fairer." ✨🪞
👑😡🔪🌲 "Kill her!" 🌲🔪😡👑
🏃‍♂️🌲🐿️🦌🐇 Snow White runs! 🐇🦌🐿️🌲
🏠🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️ She finds a cottage. 🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🏠
🛌💤🍎👵🎃 The Queen disguises herself. 🎃👵🍎💤🛌
🍎👄💀 "Take a bite." 💀👄🍎
💤💤💤 Snow White falls into a deep sleep. 💤💤💤
⚰️🌲🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️ The dwarfs mourn. 🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♂️🧚‍♀️🌲⚰️
🤴🐎🏰 The Prince arrives. 🏰🐎🤴
💋💥🍎💨 He kisses her, the apple dislodges! 💨🍎💥💋
👀✨💖 She wakes up! 💖✨👀
